{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/2f/c6/29210_crt_49uQ4.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2f/c6/29210_crt_49uQ4.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/2f/c6/29210_crt_49uQ4.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/2f/c6/29210_crt_49uQ4.jpg"},"name":"有栖川徹子","summary":"","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/82/9e/13102_prsn_zo9UU.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/82/9e/13102_prsn_zo9UU.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/82/9e/13102_prsn_zo9UU.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/82/9e/13102_prsn_zo9UU.jpg"},"name":"蒼井優","short_summary":"苍井优（1985年8月17日—）、日本女演员，本名夏井优，出身于日本福冈县。\r\n身高160厘米，血型为A型，隶属Itoh Company事务所。","career":["seiyu","actor"],"id":13102,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":29210},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/92/8c/29211_crt_ZN4bd.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/92/8c/29211_crt_ZN4bd.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/92/8c/29211_crt_ZN4bd.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/92/8c/29211_crt_ZN4bd.jpg"},"name":"荒井花","summary":"","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/0e/b5/4553_prsn_aL5ZQ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/0e/b5/4553_prsn_aL5ZQ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/0e/b5/4553_prsn_aL5ZQ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/0e/b5/4553_prsn_aL5ZQ.jpg"},"name":"鈴木杏","short_summary":"鈴木 杏（すずき あん、1987年4月27日 - ）は、日本の女優、元子役。本名同じ。愛称はあんこ、ネロ。東京都世田谷区出身。フォスタープラス所属。\r\n\r\n小学生の頃から子役として芸能活動をしており、同年代の芸能人に比べると比較的芸歴は長い。蜷川幸雄演出作品にも数多く起用されるなど、実力派の女優として知られている。一般には、ローソンや大塚製薬の「ポカリスエット」のCMで、注目されるようになった。\r\n\r\n1996年7月、『金田一少年の事件簿（第2シーズン）』で都築瑞穂役ドラマデビュー。翌年、ドラマ『青い鳥』に出演し注目を浴びる。\r\n\r\n2003年、蒼井優とW主演を務めた『花とアリス』がネット配信された後、話題を呼び2004年に劇場公開される。2005年7月、『がんばっていきまっしょい』にて再び注目を集める。\r\n\r\n2006年に堀越高等学校卒業、和光大学現代人間学部に進学。\r\n\r\n2009年12月14日、鳩山由紀夫主催の、習近平歓迎晩餐会に出席。公式ブログの中で、招待されたことへの驚きを綴っている。\r\n\r\n2015年5月17日より、NHK大河ドラマ『花燃ゆ』で広末涼子の代役として辰路役を演じる。\r\n\r\n2021年2月9日、第28回読売演劇大賞にて大賞および最優秀女優賞を受賞。","career":["seiyu","actor"],"id":4553,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":29211},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/4d/65/138453_crt_OkuJI.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4d/65/138453_crt_OkuJI.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/4d/65/138453_crt_OkuJI.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/4d/65/138453_crt_OkuJI.jpg"},"name":"有栖川加代","summary":"彻子的母亲。","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/31/72/57204_prsn_24TRL.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/31/72/57204_prsn_24TRL.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/31/72/57204_prsn_24TRL.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/31/72/57204_prsn_24TRL.jpg"},"name":"相田翔子","short_summary":"","career":["artist","seiyu","actor"],"id":57204,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":138453}],"detail":[{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"female","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/92/8c/29211_crt_ZN4bd.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/92/8c/29211_crt_ZN4bd.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/92/8c/29211_crt_ZN4bd.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/92/8c/29211_crt_ZN4bd.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"荒井花","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"荒井花"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"英文名","v":"Hana Arai"},{"k":"日文名","v":"荒井花"},{"k":"纯假名","v":"あらい はな"},{"k":"昵称","v":"花"}]},{"key":"性别","value":"女"},{"key":"引用来源","value":"http://myanimelist.net/character/115819/Hana_Arai"}],"stat":{"comments":5,"collects":19},"id":29211,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"female","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/4d/65/138453_crt_OkuJI.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4d/65/138453_crt_OkuJI.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/4d/65/138453_crt_OkuJI.jpg","medium":"https: